By running the cmd **Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope Process -ExecutionPolicy Bypass**, I'm able to retrieve the aad-token without any issues in the PowerShell.

This is the [link](https://medium.com/@caiomsouza/fix-for-powershell-script-not-digitally-signed-69f0ed518715) to the same.
